			<title>NvP 7x03 - Forbidden Island with Matt Leacock</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/JVvJzZot5mM/nv-p-7x03-forbidden-island-with-matt-leacock</link>
            <description>&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/133031677382/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-626f4eabfd5fb934.m4v"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this episode we discuss the game &lt;a href="http://www.gamewright.com/gamewright/index.php?section=games&amp;amp;page=game&amp;amp;show=245" target="_blank"&gt;Forbidden Island&lt;/a&gt; with designer Matt Leacock. We explore the ways that Forbidden Island creates a constant sense of urgency pushing players to consistently re-evaluate their strategy to win the game.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To learn more about Forbidden Island click &lt;a href="http://www.gamewright.com/gamewright/index.php?section=games&amp;amp;page=game&amp;amp;show=245" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/JVvJzZot5mM" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
