			<title>NvP 7x02 - Kamakura with Alex Montgomery</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/Qmc9hLR1054/nv-p-7x02-kamakura-with-alex-montgomery</link>
            <description>&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/132980668691/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-849052bbe079eef0.m4v"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this episode we learn about a relatively unknown game that takes minutes to play, but provides many hours of fun. The game is &lt;a href="http://dyadgames.com/games/index.html" target="_blank"&gt;Kamakura&lt;/a&gt;, and its designer is Alex Montgomery. We explore the various levels of strategy that the game affords players who may be looking for a quick and easy game to pass the time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To find out more about the game, &lt;a href="http://dyadgames.com/games/index.html" target="_blank"&gt;click here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
