			<title>NvP 7x01 - Founding Fathers with Christian Leonhard and Jason Matthews</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/hAh5f2KoFYM/nv-p-7x01-founding-fathers-with-christian-leonhard-and-jason-matthews</link>
            <description>&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/132847706625/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-74236115e571da6b.m4v"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Welcome back to the Ninja vs Pirates Podcast. We are kicking off our seventh season with our first interview of two designers at once. In this episode we interview Christian Leonhard and Jason Matthews about their game &lt;em&gt;Founding Fathers&lt;/em&gt;. We delve into the challenges that come with creating a card-driven game that relies heavily on history. We also learn a lot about the time of the creation of the Constitution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You may discover more about this game at &lt;a href="http://www.jollyrogergames.com/index.php?main_page=product_info&amp;amp;products_id=23&amp;amp;zenid=7dfecd4aaefebc3c74eac878e863f40d" target="_blank"&gt;Jolly Games&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="http://www.boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/37358/founding-fathers" target="_blank"&gt;BGG&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/hAh5f2KoFYM" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
