        <item>
			<title>NvP 6x07 - GURPS Action! with Sean Punch (a.k.a. Dr. Kromm) part 2</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/WstDvqa3ODY/nv-p-6x07-gurps-action-with-sean-punch-a-k-a-dr-kromm-part-2</link>
            <description>&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/130707186875/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-75b6d63a438ca991.m4v"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this episode we discuss one of the new GURPS line titled &lt;em&gt;Action!&lt;/em&gt; Sean discusses how this iteration of the GURPS system aims to bring the players into their very own action movie. We explore the ins and outs of the system as well as the influences that Sean sought to bring players such an exciting version of GURPS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information or to buy the game, click &lt;a href="http://www.sjgames.com/gurps/books/action/" target="_blank"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/WstDvqa3ODY" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
