			<title>NvP 6x06 - GURPS with Dr. Kromm (Sean Punch) part 1</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/W4LK1wFpMWk/nv-p-6x06-gurps-with-dr-kromm-sean-punch-part-1</link>
