&lt;p&gt;In this first-half episode we discuss the latest and one of the most exciting games from role-playing game designer extraordinaire, Vincent Baker. &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href="http://apocalypse-world.com/" target="_blank"&gt;Apocalypse World&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/em&gt;is a futuristic world that puts the action in the players hand with a GM style that feeds off of the players own energy. We discuss the GM style of the game, the plethora of "playbooks" that a player may consider choosing and even why this game has rules that encourages characters to have sex with each other.&lt;/p&gt;
