			<title>NvP 6x01 - Hoopla with Alan Pruzan</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/BSmBVjrNUrw/nv-p-6x01-hoopla-with-alan-pruzan</link>
