            <description>&lt;script src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/128330542655/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-01156a5919455a74.m4v" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://misspentyouthgame.com/"&gt;Misspent Youth&lt;/a&gt; is a story game about 12-18 year olds fighting back against the authority. We discuss with Robert his intentions for the game and how he uses the rules to enforce the feeling of being a clique of teens in a harsh world.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/OB_H0pMXwZI" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
