        <item>
			<title>NvP 5x01 - Smallville RPG with Josh Roby</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/MTlPEsOIm4I/nv_p_5x01_smallville_rpg_with_josh_roby</link>
            <description>&lt;script src="http://player.wizzard.tv/player/o/j/x/128336718189/config/k-4cb6dae3d64667e8/uuid/root/height/300/width/300/episode/k-b20adaab98c1df94.m4v" type="text/javascript"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this episode we do a preview episode with Josh Roby. We discuss his game, the Smallville RPG. This game is going to be released at GenCon!!! Smallville is unique for a game based on a property. Number one, yes you can be Superman; number two, the game is set in a TV show spin off of smallville the tv show, not in the world if Smallville were real!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We discuss the nuances of working with a property, how to balance Superman with... non-Superman characters and how the game rules support the tv show dynamic.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/MTlPEsOIm4I" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
