&lt;p&gt;In this episode we talk about &lt;a href="http://www.wunderland.com/LooneyLabs/Traitor/index.html"&gt;Are You the Traitor&lt;/a&gt; with Andrew Looney of &lt;a href="http://www.looneylabs.com/"&gt;Looney Labs&lt;/a&gt;. Are You the Traitor is a party game for 4 - 10+ people where the object is to find the traitor. The game is very similar to the popular party game Werewolf(aka Mafia). In fact Are you the Traitor was inspired by Werewolf. Andy said, i love Werewolf, but i could make it better. We talk to him about how to "fix" a game that you really love.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~4/fis7pW711-E" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description>
