        <item>
			<title>NvP 3x05 - The Mountain Witch with Timothy Walters Kleinert</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/XGlLByLqoSc/nv_p_3x05_the_mountain_witch_with_timothy_walters_kleinert</link>
            <description>We discuss the Indie RPG &lt;a href='http://www.indiepressrevolution.com/xcart/product.php?productid=16224&amp;cat=0&amp;page=1'&gt;The Mountain Witch&lt;/a&gt; with its designer Timothy Walters Kleinert. We ask him about how he designed some of the very unique elements of the game; specifily how he turned player-vs-player conflict into a fun time, how he made splitting the party actually a good thing, and how he solved the problem of meta game knowledge.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
We also talk to Tim about his planned projects, but you have listen to find out!

