			<title>NvP 3x04 - Pirates of the Spanish Main with Mike Selinker</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/HAd0VxvcNJM/nv_p_3x04_pirates_of_the_spanish_main_with_mike_selinker</link>
            <description>We discuss the card game &lt;a href='http://www.lonesharkgames.com'&gt;Pirates of the Spanish Main&lt;/a&gt; with its co-designer Mike Selinker. We discuss the challenges in creating a self-contained collectible card game.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
