			<title>NvP 2x02 - The Several Journeys of Remus with Jay Ziebarth</title>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/NinjaVsPirates/~3/XljzZuVvpoo/nv_p_2x02_the_several_journeys_of_remus_with_jay_ziebarth</link>
            <description>Jay Ziebarth is the owner of and designer at &lt;a href="http://www.ziebarf.com"&gt;Zeebarf.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.zeebarf.com/games.html"&gt;The Several Journeys of Remus&lt;/a&gt; is a series of point and click adventure games. You take on the persona of Remus and his side kick Liam in a surreal magical world. You must point and click your way to the end of the story in true Lucas Arts fashion.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;We heavily discuss feedback with Jay. Adventure games are a genre where balancing feedback is of utmost importance. Too much and the key aesthetic of challenge disappears, too little and frustration sets in. We ask Jay about how he tackles this key design challenge.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;

